name: Flying WestJet's TRANSATLANTIC Business Class! 787-9 Dublin to Calgary
description:
In June last year, WestJet launched non-stop flights between Calgary, Alberta, and Dublin, Ireland, with their then-brand-new 787-9 Dreamliners!

On this flight, I had the privilege of being able to fly in their transatlantic Business Class. See what I thought of it in this new trip report!

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

DISCLAIMER: This was a complimentary upgrade from WestJet from Economy Class to Business Class. This video was not pre-approved by WestJet and all opinions are my own.
